<sect2>
<title>安装 <application>Nail</application></title>

<para>安装<application>Nail</application> 可以使用下面命令：
(注意：如果你想把nail连接到<application>openssl </application>库，就在configure命令后面加上<userinput>--with-openssl</userinput>参数。)</para>

<screen><userinput><command>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install &amp;&amp;
ln -sf nail /usr/bin/mail</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>
